{"main_category": "All Beauty", "title": "Kungfu Apothecary - Facial Cupping Set", "average_rating": 5.0, "rating_number": 2, "features": ["Lift, plump and minimize wrinkles on your face and d\u00e9colletage naturally with our medical grade silicone cupping set", "Cupping is an ancient modality used for centuries to cure muscle aches, pain and other ailments", "Our facial cups are designed specifically to enhance the face, neck and jawline by boosting cellular turnover, promoting circulation, and lifting and plumping the face"], "description": ["Lift, plump and minimize wrinkles on your face and d\u00e9colletage naturally with our medical grade silicone cupping set . Cupping is an ancient modality used for centuries to cure muscle aches, pain and other ailments. Our facial cups are designed specifically to enhance the face, neck and jawline by boosting cellular turnover, promoting circulation, and lifting and plumping the face. How to Use: After cleansing, warm your preferred facial oil in your hands and apply to the entire face. This is a necessary step to provide \"slip\" and ensure the cup will move easily across the face. The first technique is the sweeping technique; gently squeeze the large cup on both sides, apply to skin and release to create suction. Use this squeeze and release technique in light sweeping strokes in an upward motion, from chin to temple. The second technique is the staccato technique; squeeze the large cup in an area you want to focus on (jawline, cheek, 11 lines, smile lines, etc) and squeeze and release the cup in short, quick bursts. The small cups are very useful for targeting the delicate eyes and lips.
